relation: Make sure you take care of your teeth, too!

That's right, say "fuzzy pickles" for me, kid. This is another experiment. If it looks worse than my other drawings up to this point, it's because I drew this entirely with my non-dominant hand. Very little erasing, as well.
Or maybe, "sllkk", whatever that slurping noise sounds like.
My, what big teeth you have...
